<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-4898] Pattern-colored stencil mask not interpolating when scaling</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4898</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In PageDrawer.drawImage() there is code (strategy created in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1958&quot; title=&quot;image mask outline with shading pattern is invisible&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1958&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1958&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) where an image is a stencil and the color space is a pattern. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2171&quot; title=&quot;UnsupportedOperationException for stencil image / pattern&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2171&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2171&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-002-002710-p14.pdf has two areas that have rendered poorly for years, the &quot;New Harmony Consolidated&quot; and &quot;Clay City Consolidated&quot; patterns.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using the rendering hints of the &quot;parent&quot; graphics device improves this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
